fields.name: value
fields.comment: Has the current text being edited on the textbox.

fields.name: canLoseFocus
fields.comment: if true the textbox can lose focus by clicking elsewhere on the screen

fields.name: isEditable
fields.comment: If this value is true along with isFocused, keyTyped will process the keys.

fields.name: displayPos
fields.comment: The current character index that should be used as start of the rendered text.

fields.name: highlightPos
fields.comment: other selection position, maybe the same as the cursor

fields.name: filter
fields.comment: Called to check if the text is valid

fields.name: visible
fields.comment: Weither or not the playerlist is currently being rendered
